        <Parent_String>light absorption measuring devices [300196715], light measuring devices [300195756], measuring devices for phenomena [300195703], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
